of our ancient ancestral

00:03:53.630 --> 00:03:55.400 align:middle line:84%
baggage that we
might carry-- even

00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:57.530 align:middle line:84%
the baggage from this
life, our trauma,

00:03:57.530 --> 00:04:00.950 align:middle line:84%
our injuries-- they all show up
