00:04:00.950 --> 00:04:02.280 align:middle line:90%
way in our body.

00:04:02.280 --> 00:04:04.010 align:middle line:84%
And that makes it
more fun and more

00:04:04.010 --> 00:04:07.610 align:middle line:84%
engaging to be able to go back
into, what is our posture?

00:04:07.610 --> 00:04:09.050 align:middle line:90%
Where are we at now?

00:04:09.050 --> 00:04:11.090 align:middle line:84%
We start there and
then we start moving

00:04:11.090 --> 00:04:13.040 align:middle line:84%
in the direction of
not just healing,

00:04:13.040 --> 00:04:15.050 align:middle line:84%
but healing will be
the emergent quality

00:04:15.050 --> 00:04:18.740 align:middle line:84%
of coming back into alignment
with where is our center?

00:04:18.740 --> 00:04:22.430 align:middle line:84%
Where is our center of movement
