00:04:50.990 --> 00:04:52.250 align:middle line:90%
What is center for us.

00:04:52.250 --> 00:04:53.510 align:middle line:90%
What is healing for us.

00:04:53.510 --> 00:04:56.270 align:middle line:84%
What is actually balance
