00:05:57.270 --> 00:05:59.010 align:middle line:90%
of becoming very rigid.

00:05:59.010 --> 00:06:02.160 align:middle line:84%
And in a sense, building
economic models and things

00:06:02.160 --> 00:06:05.630 align:middle line:84%
that are very rigid around
an idea that-- like you

00:06:05.630 --> 00:06:07.380 align:middle line:84%
