00:06:36.810 --> 00:06:38.894 align:middle line:84%
if we feel that
balance is needed.

00:06:38.894 --> 00:06:41.310 align:middle line:84%
And it's the same thing with
both hemispheres of the body.

00:06:41.310 --> 00:06:42.870 align:middle line:90%
We are symmetrical.

00:06:42.870 --> 00:06:45.060 align:middle line:84%
And we have two
hemispheres of the body.

00:06:45.060 --> 00:06:46.740 align:middle line:90%
And let's say-- for instance--

00:06:46.740 --> 00:06:48.870 align:middle line:84%
I broke my right
ankle when I was 12

00:06:48.870 --> 00:06:50.760 align:middle line:84%
