00:06:57.870 --> 00:07:00.090 align:middle line:84%
So there is this
asynchrony that was

00:07:00.090 --> 00:07:03.840 align:middle line:84%
building because this leg
was getting much smaller.

00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:06.420 align:middle line:84%
So I had to then,
work on my gait cycle

00:07:06.420 --> 00:07:10.440 align:middle line:84%
and how I walk because the more
that I realized as I got later

00:07:10.440 --> 00:07:13.350 align:middle line:84%
and I started looking at
what can a improper gait

00:07:13.350 --> 00:07:15.280 align:middle line:90%
cycle actually do to you--

00:07:15.280 --> 00:07:18.760 align:middle line:84%
it actually affects you all
the way up into the inside

00:07:18.760 --> 00:07:19.810 align:middle line:90%
of your cranium.

00:07:19.810 --> 00:07:20.610 align:middle line:90%
basically.

00:07:20.610 --> 00:07:23.620 align:middle line:84%
You have this sphenoid bone
and it looks like an owl.

00:07:23.620 --> 00:07:25.860 align:middle line:84%
If you were to take off
the front part of the face,

00:07:25.860 --> 00:07:27.630 align:middle line:84%
it's this thing that
when you're walking,

00:07:27.630 --> 00:07:30.120 align:middle line:84%
it actually like
moves back and forth--

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:32.130 align:middle line:90%
or it even flaps its wings.

00:07:32.130 --> 00:07:35.760 align:middle line:84%
And that houses the pituitary
gland and the pineal gland.

00:07:35.760 --> 00:07:39.870 align:middle line:84%
And so not having a proper
gait cycle or a walking form,

00:07:39.870 --> 00:07:43.800 align:middle line:84%
actually can degrade
the operation

00:07:43.800 --> 00:07:46.740 align:middle line:84%
of the pituitary gland,
which is the master gland.

00:07:46.740 --> 00:07:49.080 align:middle line:84%
So your hormonal
balance, your attitude,

00:07:49.080 --> 00:07:51.540 align:middle line:90%
your way of perceiving yourself.

00:07:51.540 --> 00:07:54.370 align:middle line:90%
The way that you actually even--

00:07:54.370 --> 00:07:56.580 align:middle line:84%
how much potential you
think you even have.

00:07:56.580 --> 00:07:58.800 align:middle line:84%
How much impact in the
world or in your culture you

00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:00.120 align:middle line:90%
believe you have--

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:02.490 align:middle line:84%
can be actually
affected very, very much

00:08:02.490 --> 00:08:05.010 align:middle line:90%
so just by improper walking.

00:08:05.010 --> 00:08:06.150 align:middle line:90%
So we all have injuries.

00:08:06.150 --> 00:08:07.657 align:middle line:90%
We all have trauma.

00:08:07.657 --> 00:08:08.490 align:middle line:90%
And we have trauma--

00:08:08.490 --> 00:08:11.610 align:middle line:84%
you go into these contractions,
like your body contracts

00:08:11.610 --> 00:08:14.640 align:middle line:84%
