00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:19.140 align:middle line:84%
It's the same thing as an
overwhelming situation.

00:08:19.140 --> 00:08:21.360 align:middle line:84%
And when that happens,
your body will

00:08:21.360 --> 00:08:23.400 align:middle line:84%
go into a certain
contracting pattern.

00:08:23.400 --> 00:08:26.730 align:middle line:84%
And then the next time another
kind of trauma or fright

00:08:26.730 --> 00:08:30.000 align:middle line:84%
happens and you'll likely go
back to that same path of least

00:08:30.000 --> 00:08:31.150 align:middle line:90%
resistance.

00:08:31.150 --> 00:08:33.990 align:middle line:84%
So now it's symbolic,
