00:08:38.370 --> 00:08:42.130 align:middle line:84%
So I like to look at the
body is it's an art form.

00:08:42.130 --> 00:08:44.620 align:middle line:84%
And it's actually
speaking symbolically.

00:08:44.620 --> 00:08:46.960 align:middle line:84%
Because it doesn't have
the English language,

00:08:46.960 --> 00:08:49.060 align:middle line:90%
it speaks completely different.

00:08:49.060 --> 00:08:50.820 align:middle line:84%
So what I believe
this is all about

00:08:50.820 --> 00:08:52.470 align:middle line:84%
is our relationships--
coming back

00:08:52.470 --> 00:08:54.060 align:middle line:90%
in a relationship with the body.

00:08:54.060 --> 00:08:55.890 align:middle line:90%
Listening to it.

00:08:55.890 --> 00:08:58.500 align:middle line:84%
In symbolic form,
what is it telling us

00:08:58.500 --> 00:09:00.600 align:middle line:84%
