This posture says a lot.

00:09:05.640 --> 00:09:08.320 align:middle line:90%
This posture says a lot.

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:11.370 align:middle line:84%
So there's all these little
things where posture actually

00:09:11.370 --> 00:09:14.100 align:middle line:90%
