And how does that start
to change our state?

00:10:09.090 --> 00:10:12.390 align:middle line:84%
Because I think that's the piece
that can be the hook of like,

00:10:12.390 --> 00:10:13.620 align:middle line:90%
I can get curious about this.

00:10:13.620 --> 00:10:16.020 align:middle line:90%
But why?"

00:10:16.020 --> 00:10:18.630 align:middle line:90%
How can this change my state?

00:10:18.630 --> 00:10:21.240 align:middle line:84%
>> And you brought up a
bunch of really good points.

00:10:21.240 --> 00:10:24.270 align:middle line:84%
Trauma, injury--
these things happen.

00:10:24.270 --> 00:10:27.580 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that they
happen for a very good reason.

00:10:27.580 --> 00:10:31.000 align:middle line:84%
If we were always in a state of
equanimity, we wouldn't learn.

00:10:31.000 --> 00:10:33.130 align:middle line:84%
And so that's not
the point here.

00:10:33.130 --> 00:10:35.580 align:middle line:90%
We're meant to find our balance.

00:10:35.580 --> 00:10:39.030 align:middle line:84%
But life is also meant to
throw us off balance that way,

00:10:39.030 --> 00:10:41.820 align:middle line:84%
we can keep finding
our way back to balance

00:10:41.820 --> 00:10:46.050 align:middle line:84%
from all these nuance
different imbalances.

00:10:46.050 --> 00:10:47.970 align:middle line:84%
And so I think that
the inspiration

00:10:47.970 --> 00:10:49.155 align:middle line:90%
that you're speaking about--

00:10:49.155 --> 00:10:52.020 align:middle line:84%
that's really the best
part of this is because--

00:10:52.020 --> 00:10:53.130 align:middle line:90%
I'm an artist at heart.

00:10:53.130 --> 00:11:00.150 align:middle line:84%
So I use research as an element
or a color in a grand painting

00:11:00.150 --> 00:11:02.250 align:middle line:90%
or a grand masterpiece.

00:11:02.250 --> 00:11:03.635 align:middle line:90%
Whereas, a lot of people--

00:11:03.635 --> 00:11:06.570 align:middle line:84%
they need it proven to them
first before they start moving.

00:11:06.570 --> 00:11:08.520 align:middle line:90%
To me-- as an artist--

00:11:08.520 --> 00:11:10.920 align:middle line:84%
the body is already
speaking to you.

00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:13.230 align:middle line:84%
We already have a
relationship with it.

00:11:13.230 --> 00:11:17.520 align:middle line:84%
And nobody else-- you don't need
external validation to say this

00:11:17.520 --> 00:11:19.750 align:middle line:84%
is what your body
is telling you.

00:11:19.750 --> 00:11:20.880 align:middle line:90%
You can listen to people.

00:11:20.880 --> 00:11:23.010 align:middle line:84%
You can maybe allow
that to inform

00:11:23.010 --> 00:11:24.460 align:middle line:90%
how you listen to your body.

00:11:24.460 --> 00:11:27.240 align:middle line:84%
But really, you're the
best expert on your body.

00:11:27.240 --> 00:11:29.040 align:middle line:90%
I'm the best on mine.

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:30.970 align:middle line:84%
And this is the
brilliance of that.

00:11:30.970 --> 00:11:35.010 align:middle line:84%
So coming back into good
posture-- what does that mean?

00:11:35.010 --> 00:11:38.040 align:middle line:84%
That really means
that we wish to have

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:39.720 align:middle line:90%
a bit more of an optimal state.

00:11:39.720 --> 00:11:41.430 align:middle line:90%
We wish to have more balance.

00:11:41.430 --> 00:11:46.020 align:middle line:84%
We wish to have maybe less
stress-- all these things that

00:11:46.020 --> 00:11:48.630 align:middle line:84%
are typified by our
culture, causes of stress

00:11:48.630 --> 00:11:50.120 align:middle line:90%
and we want less stress.

00:11:50.120 --> 00:11:53.760 align:middle line:84%
Our job causes us injuries
so we want less injury.

00:11:53.760 --> 00:11:56.680 align:middle line:84%
It's these circumstances
that we can overcome,

00:11:56.680 --> 00:11:59.320 align:middle line:84%
but the thing is that we're
cultivating the desire

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:00.120 align:middle line:90%
to surmount.

00:12:00.120 --> 00:12:02.010 align:middle line:90%
To actually overcome them.

00:12:02.010 --> 00:12:03.150 align:middle line:90%
So that's the beauty of it.

00:12:03.150 --> 00:12:05.370 align:middle line:84%
So it's actually
looking at the body

00:12:05.370 --> 00:12:09.420 align:middle line:84%
and looking at posture
as an art form that's

00:12:09.420 --> 00:12:10.680 align:middle line:90%
constantly teaching us.

00:12:10.680 --> 00:12:14.220 align:middle line:84%
And once you overcome something,
once you wake up to something--

00:12:14.220 --> 00:12:16.500 align:middle line:84%
you don't need that alarm
bell to keep ringing.

00:12:16.500 --> 00:12:18.850 align:middle line:84%
You need to move
on from that point.

00:12:18.850 --> 00:12:20.610 align:middle line:84%
So that's really the
brilliance of it.

00:12:20.610 --> 00:12:22.860 align:middle line:84%
It's not hanging
onto these old things

00:12:22.860 --> 00:12:25.410 align:middle line:84%
and really, it doesn't
matter where the injury truly

00:12:25.410 --> 00:12:26.610 align:middle line:90%
came from.

00:12:26.610 --> 00:12:28.110 align:middle line:90%
You can still work on it.

00:12:28.110 --> 00:12:31.681 align:middle line:84%
Because I've forgotten some
of the emotional traumas

00:12:31.681 --> 00:12:33.180 align:middle line:84%
and some of the
little things that I

00:12:33.180 --> 00:12:36.520 align:middle line:84%
experienced as a little kid,
but it's here in my body.

00:12:36.520 --> 00:12:38.400 align:middle line:84%
So I'm not working on
me as a little kid,

00:12:38.400 --> 00:12:40.440 align:middle line:84%
I'm working on the
body that I have now.

00:12:40.440 --> 00:12:42.450 align:middle line:90%
And coming back into center.

00:12:42.450 --> 00:12:44.890 align:middle line:90%
How does it change our state?

00:12:44.890 --> 00:12:47.610 align:middle line:84%
Well, we know that
moving the body

00:12:47.610 --> 00:12:50.760 align:middle line:84%
and actually giving it
challenge and giving it risk

00:12:50.760 --> 00:12:53.640 align:middle line:84%
is actually a way to
enter the flow state.

00:12:53.640 --> 00:12:56.340 align:middle line:84%
So the Flow Genome Project
is talking about here's

00:12:56.340 --> 00:12:58.500 align:middle line:84%
your comfort level
of a certain task.

00:12:58.500 --> 00:13:01.740 align:middle line:84%
If you go 4% more,
then you're already

00:13:01.740 --> 00:13:03.270 align:middle line:90%
triggering the flow state.

00:13:03.270 --> 00:13:05.250 align:middle line:84%
So challenge and
risk are two things

00:13:05.250 --> 00:13:08.250 align:middle line:84%
that trigger a different
altered state of consciousness

00:13:08.250 --> 00:13:11.190 align:middle line:84%
that I believe is actually
accessing what you would call

00:13:11.190 --> 00:13:13.130 align:middle line:90%
the quantum realm inside you.

00:13:13.130 --> 00:13:17.250 align:middle line:84%
And that's a realm of
really, pure magic.

00:13:17.250 --> 00:13:19.970 align:middle line:84%
So there's a lot of things
that quantum physics

00:13:19.970 --> 00:13:23.850 align:middle line:84%
is breaking down of the
old science, the old idea

00:13:23.850 --> 00:13:26.490 align:middle line:84%
that we've come from where
everything is so rigid.

00:13:26.490 --> 00:13:28.860 align:middle line:90%
So the body-- it wants to learn.

00:13:28.860 --> 00:13:31.500 align:middle line:84%
And it does that by
being thrown off balance,

00:13:31.500 --> 00:13:33.370 align:middle line:90%
coming back into balance.

00:13:33.370 --> 00:13:36.600 align:middle line:84%
So I say, the best thing
that we can actually do--

00:13:36.600 --> 00:13:38.970 align:middle line:84%
the states that we can
find ourselves in--

00:13:38.970 --> 00:13:42.660 align:middle line:84%
is finding what the
body is telling us.

00:13:42.660 --> 00:13:44.280 align:middle line:90%
Looking at our posture.

00:13:44.280 --> 00:13:48.750 align:middle line:84%
Not harping on ourselves or
getting down on ourselves

00:13:48.750 --> 00:13:50.970 align:middle line:84%
because our posture
isn't perfect.

00:13:50.970 --> 00:13:52.260 align:middle line:90%
You start where you are.

00:13:52.260 --> 00:13:54.270 align:middle line:84%
You forgive yourself
for all of the past.

00:13:54.270 --> 00:13:57.030 align:middle line:84%
You forgive your parents
and everybody who you feel

00:13:57.030 --> 00:13:58.170 align:middle line:90%
has wronged you.

00:13:58.170 --> 00:14:01.830 align:middle line:84%
And you start in this moment
to move back in the direction,

00:14:01.830 --> 00:14:04.680 align:middle line:84%
back in the trajectory
of what you feel balanced

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:06.330 align:middle line:90%
and what you for your health is.

00:14:06.330 --> 00:14:09.330 align:middle line:84%
So it is really a personal
journey for each of us.

00:14:09.330 --> 00:14:11.310 align:middle line:90%
And the body is--

00:14:11.310 --> 00:14:12.390 align:middle line:90%
it's our guide.

00:14:12.390 --> 00:14:13.590 align:middle line:90%
It really is our guide.

00:14:13.590 --> 00:14:16.890 align:middle line:84%
It's whispering to
us in symbolic form.

00:14:16.890 --> 00:14:19.020 align:middle line:84%
And if we learn how
to listen to that,

00:14:19.020 --> 00:14:21.630 align:middle line:84%
we are the ones that
are meeting it halfway.

00:14:21.630 --> 00:14:25.770 align:middle line:84%
So us actually consciously
changing our posture,

00:14:25.770 --> 00:14:27.870 align:middle line:84%
us actually consciously
changing the way

00:14:27.870 --> 00:14:33.000 align:middle line:84%
that we move into a more
intelligent, graceful manner--

00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:35.550 align:middle line:84%
that's where we're really going
to start hearing the deeper

00:14:35.550 --> 00:14:38.580 align:middle line:84%
messages of life that
don't speak God's not

00:14:38.580 --> 00:14:40.830 align:middle line:84%
going to peek through the
clouds and actually tell you

00:14:40.830 --> 00:14:41.940 align:middle line:90%
the secrets.

00:14:41.940 --> 00:14:43.200 align:middle line:90%
This is the riddle.

00:14:43.200 --> 00:14:44.430 align:middle line:90%
This is the enigma.

00:14:44.430 --> 00:14:46.380 align:middle line:84%
So if we listen to
it, it will actually

00:14:46.380 --> 00:14:47.910 align:middle line:90%
reveal its secrets to us.

00:14:47.910 --> 00:14:49.560 align:middle line:90%
But there is the key.

00:14:49.560 --> 00:14:52.940 align:middle line:84%
All relationships-- your lovers,
your children, your family,

00:14:52.940 --> 00:14:54.360 align:middle line:90%
nature in general--

00:14:54.360 --> 00:14:57.480 align:middle line:84%
you have to listen to come into
a better relationship with it.

00:14:57.480 --> 00:14:59.460 align:middle line:90%
Force does not work.

00:14:59.460 --> 00:15:01.420 align:middle line:90%
Ignoring it does not work.

00:15:01.420 --> 00:15:04.080 align:middle line:84%
You have to meet it
halfway, actually listen.

00:15:04.080 --> 00:15:05.850 align:middle line:84%
And this will change
your conscious state

00:15:05.850 --> 00:15:07.950 align:middle line:84%
and actually bring
you into a state

00:15:07.950 --> 00:15:11.340 align:middle line:84%
where you feel confident that
you can listen to the body

00:15:11.340 --> 00:15:14.370 align:middle line:84%
and it's actually giving
you the tips and clues

00:15:14.370 --> 00:15:18.120 align:middle line:84%
to move towards
healing and wholeness.

00:15:18.120 --> 00:15:24.200 align:middle line:84%
>> I love this because we've
heard a lot that meditation can

00:15:24.200 --> 00:15:27.080 align:middle line:90%
start to calm the mind.

00:15:27.080 --> 00:15:30.470 align:middle line:84%
And that calming the mind
can start to relieve stress.

00:15:30.470 --> 00:15:32.130 align:middle line:90%
Can start to relieve pain.

00:15:32.130 --> 00:15:34.760 align:middle line:84%
And I think an important piece
that we shouldn't overlook

00:15:34.760 --> 00:15:39.440 align:middle line:84%
is that also, by moving
in more conscious ways

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:42.110 align:middle line:84%
and actually being in the
body in more conscious ways--

00:15:42.110 --> 00:15:44.570 align:middle line:84%
also works the mind
and comes the mind.

00:15:44.570 --> 00:15:46.310 align:middle line:84%
That it can work
in both directions.

00:15:46.310 --> 00:15:51.110 align:middle line:84%
So I'd love to have you show
us a couple of things about,

00:15:51.110 --> 00:15:54.380 align:middle line:84%
how can we start
to learn to listen?

00:15:54.380 --> 00:15:58.820 align:middle line:84%
How can we start to change
these states and tune

00:15:58.820 --> 00:16:03.590 align:middle line:84%
into this deeper wisdom that
our body is offering us?

00:16:03.590 --> 00:16:04.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Absolutely.

00:16:04.390 --> 00:16:06.130 align:middle line:90%
[WHOOSH]

00:16:06.130 --> 00:16:06.930 align:middle line:90%


00:16:06.930 --> 00:16:10.770 align:middle line:84%
First thing I'll have us do is
just check in with our posture.

00:16:10.770 --> 00:16:12.960 align:middle line:84%
Before we correct
anything, I want

00:16:12.960 --> 00:16:15.870 align:middle line:84%
us to be able to listen to
what the body's actually saying

00:16:15.870 --> 00:16:17.677 align:middle line:84%
and develop that kind
of a relationship.

00:16:17.677 --> 00:16:19.260 align:middle line:84%
And this is something
we should really

00:16:19.260 --> 00:16:22.470 align:middle line:84%
be doing throughout the
day is checking in with how

00:16:22.470 --> 00:16:23.610 align:middle line:90%
we're holding ourselves.

00:16:23.610 --> 00:16:27.420 align:middle line:84%
And remember that it's
symbolic towards how we feel.

00:16:27.420 --> 00:16:30.100 align:middle line:84%
And what we're actually
giving back out.

00:16:30.100 --> 00:16:33.610 align:middle line:84%
So the first thing is
if you're sitting--

00:16:33.610 --> 00:16:35.470 align:middle line:84%
instead of resting
against the back,

00:16:35.470 --> 00:16:37.480 align:middle line:90%
just come up a little bit.

00:16:37.480 --> 00:16:42.640 align:middle line:84%
And then adopt just a relaxed
or a slouching position.

00:16:42.640 --> 00:16:45.430 align:middle line:84%
You could even put
the hand on the legs,

00:16:45.430 --> 00:16:48.950 align:middle line:90%
but just relax into this.

00:16:48.950 --> 00:16:49.970 align:middle line:90%
Listen to the body.

00:16:49.970 --> 00:16:52.970 align:middle line:90%


00:16:52.970 --> 00:16:55.280 align:middle line:84%
Start feeling how
your breath feels.

00:16:55.280 --> 00:16:58.430 align:middle line:90%


00:16:58.430 --> 00:17:00.895 align:middle line:84%
Is it restricted in any way
because of this posture?

00:17:00.895 --> 00:17:05.859 align:middle line:90%


00:17:05.859 --> 00:17:07.990 align:middle line:84%
Now start checking in
with parts of your body--

00:17:07.990 --> 00:17:09.099 align:middle line:90%
maybe your pelvis.

00:17:09.099 --> 00:17:11.710 align:middle line:84%
Maybe your back-- that's
doing all the work

00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:13.450 align:middle line:90%
and holding this posture.

00:17:13.450 --> 00:17:15.130 align:middle line:84%
Where is all the
work being done?

00:17:15.130 --> 00:17:16.629 align:middle line:84%
And just check in
with those places.

00:17:16.629 --> 00:17:19.670 align:middle line:90%


00:17:19.670 --> 00:17:22.940 align:middle line:90%
Keep breathing.

00:17:22.940 --> 00:17:26.630 align:middle line:84%
And now, I want you to link it
to something emotional-- maybe

00:17:26.630 --> 00:17:30.050 align:middle line:84%
a strained relationship,
or a feeling

00:17:30.050 --> 00:17:33.680 align:middle line:84%
of inadequacy, a lack of
self-confidence-- whatever

00:17:33.680 --> 00:17:35.572 align:middle line:90%
it might be.

00:17:35.572 --> 00:17:37.280 align:middle line:84%
And link it to something
that's very real

00:17:37.280 --> 00:17:40.160 align:middle line:90%
and present for you lately.

00:17:40.160 --> 00:17:42.860 align:middle line:84%
Does it come up at
all in your body?

00:17:42.860 --> 00:17:45.800 align:middle line:84%
Does it feel like it
is housed or located

00:17:45.800 --> 00:17:48.800 align:middle line:90%
in any specific place?

00:17:48.800 --> 00:17:50.770 align:middle line:84%
And just keep
checking in with it.

00:17:50.770 --> 00:17:51.940 align:middle line:90%
We don't have to shame it.

00:17:51.940 --> 00:17:55.570 align:middle line:84%
We don't have to make it seem
like it's a problem, an issue.

00:17:55.570 --> 00:17:56.890 align:middle line:90%
It just is what it is.

00:17:56.890 --> 00:18:00.910 align:middle line:84%
We're already living with
it so it is what it is.

00:18:00.910 --> 00:18:03.070 align:middle line:84%
Now, we're letting
it express itself.

00:18:03.070 --> 00:18:05.810 align:middle line:90%
We're listening to it.

00:18:05.810 --> 00:18:10.850 align:middle line:84%
And the more you breathe and
just check in with your body,

00:18:10.850 --> 00:18:13.575 align:middle line:84%
just see where your
attention goes naturally.

00:18:13.575 --> 00:18:16.989 align:middle line:90%


00:18:16.989 --> 00:18:18.530 align:middle line:84%
And once you've come
to a state where

00:18:18.530 --> 00:18:22.430 align:middle line:84%
you feel like you've actually
received some kind of message

00:18:22.430 --> 00:18:25.580 align:middle line:84%
and then remember-- you've
already received the message.

00:18:25.580 --> 00:18:29.360 align:middle line:84%
It's just not in a language
that you fully understand.

00:18:29.360 --> 00:18:32.310 align:middle line:84%
And this is where the
creativity comes in.

00:18:32.310 --> 00:18:34.370 align:middle line:84%
So once you get to that
place where you feel that

00:18:34.370 --> 00:18:36.710 align:middle line:84%
you've received the message--
whether you can put it

00:18:36.710 --> 00:18:38.420 align:middle line:90%
into words or not--

00:18:38.420 --> 00:18:41.632 align:middle line:84%
then I'd invite you
to sit up straight.

00:18:41.632 --> 00:18:44.090 align:middle line:84%
Just whatever that means to
you because sitting up straight

00:18:44.090 --> 00:18:47.282 align:middle line:84%
also means something
different to everybody.

00:18:47.282 --> 00:18:49.240 align:middle line:84%
And as you're sitting
straight, the first thing

00:18:49.240 --> 00:18:52.360 align:middle line:84%
I want you to do is just
roll each shoulder back one

00:18:52.360 --> 00:18:53.860 align:middle line:90%
at a time.

00:18:53.860 --> 00:18:58.470 align:middle line:84%
And then just see how your
shoulder sits at that point.

00:18:58.470 --> 00:19:01.060 align:middle line:84%
And then I want you to lift
your chin just a little bit,

00:19:01.060 --> 00:19:04.300 align:middle line:84%
just so you're not bringing
your neck down to your chest.

00:19:04.300 --> 00:19:06.610 align:middle line:84%
Just lift your chin
up a little bit

00:19:06.610 --> 00:19:10.200 align:middle line:84%
and just feel the position
of your spine, now.

00:19:10.200 --> 00:19:11.530 align:middle line:90%
Check in with your breath.

00:19:11.530 --> 00:19:12.640 align:middle line:90%
How does it feel now?

00:19:12.640 --> 00:19:16.107 align:middle line:84%
Is it as restricted as it
was when you were slouching?

00:19:16.107 --> 00:19:19.590 align:middle line:90%


00:19:19.590 --> 00:19:23.600 align:middle line:84%
Do you feel like you
have more expansiveness?

00:19:23.600 --> 00:19:24.650 align:middle line:90%
How does it feel?

00:19:24.650 --> 00:19:27.320 align:middle line:84%
Those spots in your body that
were holding your slouching

00:19:27.320 --> 00:19:28.160 align:middle line:90%
posture--

00:19:28.160 --> 00:19:29.930 align:middle line:90%
how do they feel now?

00:19:29.930 --> 00:19:31.490 align:middle line:90%
Just check in.

00:19:31.490 --> 00:19:33.560 align:middle line:84%
Nothing's right,
nothing's wrong.

00:19:33.560 --> 00:19:35.900 align:middle line:84%
It just is what it is
and it's speaking to you.

00:19:35.900 --> 00:19:41.560 align:middle line:90%


00:19:41.560 --> 00:19:44.620 align:middle line:84%
Now I want you to check back in
with that emotional component--

00:19:44.620 --> 00:19:47.680 align:middle line:84%
that strained relationship
or whatever it was.

00:19:47.680 --> 00:19:49.870 align:middle line:90%
That feeling of self-doubt.

00:19:49.870 --> 00:19:51.650 align:middle line:90%
Just check in with it.

00:19:51.650 --> 00:19:55.840 align:middle line:84%
See how that feeling,
that idea, or concept

00:19:55.840 --> 00:19:59.150 align:middle line:90%
